  "description": "A close-up photograph showcases two orange tulips in bloom, viewed from a low angle. The tulips are partially open, revealing their inner petals and details. One tulip is in full bloom, its center prominently displayed, while the other is a bud still developing. The petals exhibit a gradient from a light apricot hue to a deeper orange towards the edges. The tulips are set against a dark background and surrounded by vibrant green leaves. They are held within a golden-yellow vase with subtle vertical stripes. The lighting creates a soft, warm atmosphere, highlighting the textures of the petals and leaves.",
